<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/22 (Sat.)The First Loneliness Minister Tackles 'the Sad Reality of Modern  Life'/Tips for sounding like a native (Mei)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=421&amp;p=439#p439"><![CDATA[
8/22 (Sat.)How the World's First Loneliness Minister( 孤獨大臣) Will Tackle 'the Sad Reality of Modern Life' /3 tips for sounding like a native speaker(Host : Mei)<br /><br /><br />#1. How the World's First Loneliness Minister( 孤獨大臣) Will Tackle 'the Sad Reality of Modern Life' <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://time.com/5248016/tracey-crouch-uk-loneliness-minister/">https://time.com/5248016/tracey-crouch- ... -minister/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1. Do you think people in Taiwan are getting lonely? If so, why?<br />2. Do you think gender plays a role in one's suffering from loneliness? And why?<br />3. In Taiwanese culture, do you think people are comfortable talking about loneliness to friends and family?<br />4. If you are assigned to be a Loneliness Minister, what kind of programs / policies / activities would you recommend to the government and the general public?<br /><br />#2. 3 tips for sounding like a native speaker<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/ChZJ1Q3GSuI">https://youtu.be/ChZJ1Q3GSuI</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1. What phonetic/words are difficult to pronounce for you?<br />2. How do you improve your English speaking skills?<br />3. After watching the video, are there any tips that you find helpful? If so, why?<br /><br /><br />---------------------<br />Agenda<br />19:00-19:30 Free Talk<br />19:30-19:40 Session 1<br />19:40-20:00 Session 2 Discussion<br />20:00-20:30 Presentation<br />20:30-20:40 Intermission &amp; Group photo<br />20:40-21:00 Session 3 Discussion<br />21:00-21:30 Presentation<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Aug 19, 2020 1:44 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
